name: The FREEMOON Token
description: The FREEMOON faucet can give out two currencies to its subscribers. One common FREE and one very rare FREEMOON (FMN). Currently, every time you claim you will get 1 FREE, and the more FREE you have the higher chance you will have to also get a FREEMOON (FMN), though the chance of this happening is extremely rare. Without FREE your chance of getting 1 FMN is 0.
